#: ../../S/splork-.rst:5
msgid "splork!"
msgstr "splork!"

#: ../../S/splork-.rst:7
msgid ""
"[Usenet; common] The sound of coffee (or other beverage) hitting the monitor"
" and/or keyboard after being forced out of the mouth via the nose (also "
"\"splorf\"). It usually follows an unexpectedly funny thing in a Usenet "
"post. Compare :ref:`snarf`\\, :ref:`CNK`\\."
msgstr ""
"[Usenet; 一般的] "
"コーヒー(または他の飲み物)が、鼻を通って口から押し出された後にモニタやキーボードに当たる音(「splorf」とも)。たいてい、Usenetの投稿で予想外におかしなことがあった後に続く。\\"
" :ref:`snarf`\\ 、\\ :ref:`CNK`\\ と比較せよ。"
